ers) are correctly configured and exchanging routes.\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\n- **Network health is otherwise normal**: all routers have EBGP sessions up, routes are exchanged correctly, and there are no link or routing anomalies.  \n- **The only fault** is the missing network interface/IP on `pc_0_0`, which prevents any traffic from or to that host.  \n\nNo further investigation of the routing fabric is required at this time.", "generation_info": {"model": "gpt-oss:20b", "created_at": "2025-12-09T22:29:26.284969175Z", "done": true, "done_reason": "stop", "total_duration": 11345624838, "load_duration": 60012365, "prompt_eval_count": 5261, "prompt_eval_duration": 321536506, "eval_count": 1088, "eval_duration": 10399848234, "model_name": "gpt-oss:20b"}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 5261, "output_tokens": 1088, "total_tokens": 6349}}
